reviewText: Excellent product and excellent seller, a real asset for Amazon

Well, don't be deceived by the cover art and labels. The motion comic part has very little motion, except for a few stock loops reused endless times
to simulate motion . Most monotonous, the story line is okay but underdeveloped. Hence an average rating. With some development, and some effort to produce more fluid and meaningful artwork  there is some potential to be a production worth having.
